post_cb({"17762632": {"CreationDate": "2013-07-20T13:14:47.097", "LastActivityDate": "2013-07-20T13:32:13.217", "LastEditorUserId": "701092", "ParentId": "17762589", "Score": "4", "Id": "17762632", "OwnerUserId": "1807864", "Body": "<p>On the same page of <a href=\"http://en.cppreference.com/w/cpp/string/basic_string/erase\" rel=\"nofollow\"><code>std::string::erase</code></a> I found these lines:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p id=\"so_17762589_17762632_0\"><strong>Exceptions</strong><br>\n  1) \u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0std::out_of_range if <code>index &gt; size()</code>.<br>\n  2-3) (none)</br></br></p>\n</blockquote>\n", "CommentCount": "2", "PostTypeId": "2", "LastEditDate": "2013-07-20T13:32:13.217"}, "17762671": {"LastActivityDate": "2013-07-20T13:19:05.093", "ParentId": "17762589", "Id": "17762671", "Score": "9", "Body": "<p>It seems to be OK, since the size of the string is <code>0</code>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p id=\"so_17762589_17762671_0\"><strong>21.4.6.5 basic_string::erase [string::erase]</strong> </p>\n<p id=\"so_17762589_17762671_1\"><code>basic_string&lt;charT,traits,Allocator&gt;&amp; erase(size_type pos = 0, size_type n = npos);</code></p>\n<p id=\"so_17762589_17762671_2\">1 Requires: <code>pos &lt;= size()</code></p>\n<p id=\"so_17762589_17762671_3\">2 Throws: out_of_range if <code>pos &gt; size()</code>.</p>\n</blockquote>\n", "CommentCount": "1", "PostTypeId": "2", "OwnerUserId": "661519", "CreationDate": "2013-07-20T13:19:05.093"}, "17762589": {"AcceptedAnswerId": "17762671", "Tags": "<c++><string><erase>", "AnswerCount": "2", "OwnerUserId": "882932", "Body": "<p>Is the behaviour of <code>std::string::erase(0)</code> is well defined on an empty string. Because <a href=\"http://en.cppreference.com/w/cpp/string/basic_string/erase\" rel=\"noreferrer\">cppreference</a> says:</p>\n<pre><code>Removes count characters starting at index.\n</code></pre>\n<p>But for an empty string, the character at index 0 does not exist.</p>\n", "CommentCount": "0", "CreationDate": "2013-07-20T13:09:38.780", "PostTypeId": "1", "LastActivityDate": "2013-07-20T13:32:13.217", "Id": "17762589", "Title": "string::erase(0) on an empty string?", "Score": "6", "ViewCount": "254"}, "bq_ids": {"n3337": {"so_17762589_17762671_1": {"section_id": 1565, "quality": 0.8, "length": 4}}}});